                           java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> queryAttributeVariableMap)
Constructor - Sets the wrapper with all of the relevant data

Parameters:
qWrappers - - Array-List of QueryWrapper used in this construction command
matcher - - The matcher used for mapping between the results and the construction pattern
nSampler - - The n-sampler used to determine the number of times that the construction command will be executed
oldNodes - - A hash-map of node-id (key) to node (value) of the old nodes (nodes existing in the model)
newNodes - - A hash-map of node-id (key) to node (value) of the new nodes to be added
queryAttributeVariableMap - - A mapping between attributes to query variables
